 complete Bible handbook）。臺北：貓頭鷹。劉述先（2003）。牟宗三先生全集出版在今日的意義。鵝湖月刊，28(11)，6- 7。歐陽教（1964）。康德的哲學與教育思想。教育研究所集刊，7，163- 274。師大教育研究所。蔡仁厚（1996）。牟宗三先生學思年譜。臺北：學生。鄭家棟（2000）。牟宗三。臺北：東大。鄺芷人（1995）。康德倫理學原理。臺北：文津。二、外文部分Beck, L. W. (1960). A commentary on Kant’s critique of practical reason. Chicago: The University of Chicago.Beck, L.W. (1989). Kant selections. New York: Macmillan.Cassirer, E. (1963). Rousseau, Kant and Goethe (J. Gutmann, P. O. Kristeller and J. H. Randall, Trans.). NY: Happer & Row. (Original work published 1944).Copleston, F. (1960). A history of philosophy, vol. VI: Wolff to Kant. Westminster & Maryland: The Newman Press.Gawthrop, R. L. (1993). Pietism and the making of eighteenth- century Prussia. New York: Cambridge University Press.Guevara, D. (2000). Kant’s theory of moral motivation. Boulder, Colo.: Westview Press.Heath, P. & Schneewind, J. B. (Eds.). (1997). Immanuel Kant lectures on ethics. Cambridge: Cambridge University Press.Hutcheson, F. (1989). A system of moral philosophy. Taipei : Hsieh chih kuang yeh ts'ung shu ch'u pan kung ssu.Inwood, M. J. (1995). Lessing, Gotthold Ephraim, in T. Honderich(Ed.), The Oxford Companion to Philosophy(pp.481). New York: Oxford University Press.Kant, I. (1899). Kant on education (A. Churton, Trans.). London: Kegan Paul, Trench, Trbner & Co. Ltd .Kant, I. (1952). The critique of judgement (J. C. Meredith, Trans.). Oxford: Clarendon Press.Kant, I. (1960). Religion within the limits of reason alone (T. M. Green & H. H. Hudson, Trans.). New York: Harper & Row.Kant, I. (1977).Werke in zwolf Banden. Frankfurt : Suhrkamp.Kant, I. (1980). The doctrine of virtue Part II of the metaphysic of morals (M. Gregor, Trans.). Philadelphia: University of Pennsylvania Press.Kant, I. (1981). Observations of the feeling of the beautiful and sublime (J. T. Goldthwait, Trans.). Berkeley, C. A.: University of California Press.Kant, I. (1992). Dreams of a spirit-seer (E. F. Goerwitz, Trans.). New York: Thoemmes Press.Kant, I. (1997). Critique 